function Start()
	
-- Spawn UE	
	if Hydra.QuestCallbackCountGet(69) == 3 then
		Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_RUTKAH, idPlayer, true, 10, 10)
	end
	
	if Hydra.QuestCallbackCountGet(69) == 6 then
		Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_VARDOK, idPlayer, true, 10, 10)
	end	

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

-- Setting up a variable to target the player for the UEs to spawn on.
	idPlayer = idActorPlayer

end
